<h3 class="h3TabContent">Pro+ Kitchen Suite</h3>
<h4>Full Height Refrigeration</h4>
<img src="images/aga/pro-plus-set-closed-225x239.jpg" alt="Pro+ Kitchen Refrigerator" class="imageFloat2" />
<p>Elegant styling and state-of-the-art engineering make this French door refrigerator the perfect match for your PRO+ range. A built-in filtered water dispenser, ice maker and electronic touch controls are just a few of the convenience features. Large humidity-controlled crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh and ready to eat, and the extra large deli drawer has plenty of space for all your meats and cheeses. Adjustable interior and door shelves make storage of all your favorite items easy and convenient.</p>
<p>In keeping with the sleek design, the water dispenser has been discreetly located inside the refrigerator. This internal filtered water system with easy to use push button control delivers pure refreshment whenever you want it.</p>
